{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 86939, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 14733, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "捐了50...但我很悲观...感觉50万也是杯水车薪", "timestamp": 1593917803, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 86943, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 14733, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "理论上转了就是慈善 不应该再要求人家一定捐钱 但确实不捐有点奇怪…", "timestamp": 1593917921, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 86944, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 14733, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我捐完退出再转发的，是不是看不到我的捐助记录啊..", "timestamp": 1593917919, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 86945, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 14733, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我感觉主要不是钱……如果足够多的钱就能治好的话那真的太好了，筹款也很快。但是感觉这个病的话有点难……", "timestamp": 1593917966, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 86947, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 14733, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 说是不要道德绑架，但总觉得有点那啥，特别是转发的时候说的情真意切的，你就拿十块出来也好啊.. ", "timestamp": 1593918011, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 86959, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 14733, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 是的，唉，但总想着能尽点力也好吧。感觉只转发不捐，然后又说一大堆深情的话的人，是在“消费”这件事", "timestamp": 1593918157, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 86965, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 14733, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 应该看得到吧？", "timestamp": 1593918250, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 86969, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 14733, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "五十万卖套房还是撑得下的，学长应该性命暂且能保，可以慢慢筹款，给一点尽一份力也好", "timestamp": 1593918297, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 86974, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 14733, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "其实主要是对水滴筹这种东西有点恶心(不是对患者)，以前每次看到朋友圈有人转发都会捐一点，但现在很少捐了，除非是自己比较熟，了解情况的人。", "timestamp": 1593918338, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 86985, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 14733, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 是的…不认识的人帮转不捐钱很容易理解 但认识本人又说了一堆情真意切的话但不捐钱就…很奇怪 惠而不费吗", "timestamp": 1593918433, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 86995, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 14733, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 患者叫医生改病历，这种事情你听说过吗？工伤老板出了一份钱，他还要再来水滴筹听说过吗？", "timestamp": 1593918645, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 87029, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 14733, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有可能是匿名捐的…自己捐了就好也别想别人了（", "timestamp": 1593919016, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 87030, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 14733, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 宁说的对", "timestamp": 1593919032, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 87038, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 14733, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "可能是看不到吧，我捐完退出去再点别人的链接就只能看到自己的了……", "timestamp": 1593919104, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 4, "pid": 14733, "reply": 14, "tag": null, "text": "对于只转发不捐钱的人怎么看... 经济有限，五块十块都是钱吧... ", "timestamp": 1593917728, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1606782588, "url": "", "vote": {}}}